LiCl scf calculation
&control
    calculation  = 'scf'
    prefix       = 'licl'
    outdir       = './tmp'
    wf_collect   = .true.
/

&system
    ibrav        = 2
    celldm(1)    = 9.693
    nat          = 2
    ntyp         = 2
    ecutwfc      = 27.0
    force_symmorphic = .true.
/

&electrons
    conv_thr =  1.0d-8
/
ATOMIC_SPECIES
Li    6.941  Li.pz-n-vbc.UPF
Cl   35.45   Cl.pz-bhs.UPF

ATOMIC_POSITIONS (alat)
Li  0.00 0.00 0.00
Cl  0.50 0.50 0.50

K_POINTS AUTOMATIC
 2 2 2 0 0 0
